{"tid":2383586,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院議長Nancy Pelosi丈夫 買入特斯拉、蘋果等看漲期權","createTime":"2021-01-28T04:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T04:24:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"98afaf88ec1b03d3fe10849f3d52387715885700","tid":2383586,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:05:52.000Z","msg":"總統拜登（Joe Biden）上任，外界預測，電動車領域可望受新政府的政策提振。外媒報導指出，民主黨籍美國眾議院議長裴洛西（Nancy Pelosi）的丈夫保羅（Paul Pelosi），日前就對電動車大廠特斯拉（Tesla）押注了最多100萬美元的看漲期權，似乎相當看好特斯拉的未來。<br />\n<br />\n《福斯商業新聞》（FOX Business）報導，根據21日的財務披露資料，保羅在2020年12月22日買了25張特斯拉看漲期權，成本在50萬美元至100萬美元之間，他可在2022年3月18日到期前，以500美元行權價買入2500股特斯拉。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n另外還有蘋果公司（Apple）和華特迪士尼公司（Walt Disney Company）的看漲期權各100張，到期日皆在2022年1月21日，行權價均為100美元。蘋果成本在25萬美元至50萬美元之間，迪士尼成本在50萬美元至100萬美元之間。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3423508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3423508&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cUwaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=97d4bf78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3423508&h=05f893d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3423508</a>"},{"pid":"02554bb91b8f077fcb0a4ae37823e1aaf3bc1997","tid":2383586,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:07:41.000Z","msg":"輸死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4a1f55bac5ebbca91d0a6b925a9b6944b3333b","tid":2383586,"uid":18012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"真內幕消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62334e29a1040a2d91ac896f0de3d6fe54071db3",